# Mobile: Native iOS (Index)

## Rule files (by concern)

- `architecture.mdc`: layer boundaries (Core/Infrastructure/Presentation)
- `ui.mdc`: UI boundaries (no business logic in UI)
- `performance.mdc`: memory management, async/await, background tasks
- `networking.mdc`: URLSession, Codable, error handling
- `state.mdc`: SwiftUI state, Combine, MVVM patterns
- `error_handling.mdc`: Error types, Result types, throwing functions
- `accessibility.mdc`: VoiceOver, accessibility labels, dynamic type
- `testing.mdc`: testing expectations
- `security.mdc`: no secrets, safe logging, safe auth changes
